1
00:00:01,167 --> 00:00:02,302
I want to thank Bai Xing

2
00:00:03,470 --> 00:00:04,470
for becoming Youzhi.

3
00:00:04,971 --> 00:00:06,105
The story of him and A-You

4
00:00:06,106 --> 00:00:07,707
must have touched so many people.

5
00:00:08,308 --> 00:00:09,642
He turned past regrets

6
00:00:10,243 --> 00:00:11,277
into new possibilities.

7
00:00:11,871 --> 00:00:13,306
Falling in love is easy,

8
00:00:13,813 --> 00:00:14,981
but staying in love...

9
00:00:15,648 --> 00:00:17,050
that takes real courage.

10
00:00:17,650 --> 00:00:18,650
Thank you,

11
00:00:21,214 --> 00:00:25,952
Bai Xing.

12
00:00:31,898 --> 00:00:33,265
I want to thank Hei Yan

13
00:00:33,266 --> 00:00:34,366
for giving me the push

14
00:00:34,367 --> 00:00:35,769
to become Zhou Youzhi.

15
00:00:37,437 --> 00:00:38,605
What we have

16
00:00:39,139 --> 00:00:39,973
is more than just

17
00:00:39,974 --> 00:00:41,608
A-You and Youzhi's story.

18
00:00:42,242 --> 00:00:43,242
It's a promise.

19
00:00:43,243 --> 00:00:44,110
This isn't just acting.

20
00:00:44,111 --> 00:00:45,678
You're Black, I'm White.

21
00:00:46,312 --> 00:00:47,247
With a splash of "water,"

22
00:00:47,248 --> 00:00:48,715
"you and I" become "us."

23
00:00:51,351 --> 00:00:54,920
Kiss him!

24
00:00:54,921 --> 00:00:57,156
No, don't...

25
00:00:57,157 --> 00:01:03,096
Kiss him!

26
00:01:17,243 --> 00:01:18,578
You missed it!

27
00:01:23,082 --> 00:01:24,082
Did you get the shot?

28
00:01:24,451 --> 00:01:25,451
Thank you.
